content: Finally, you can head up the torch-lit path outside this cave guarded by many Stone Spiders. At the end of the path is a small gap leading to a room that seems to be an entrance pit of some sort, as a large green Wisp floats above a bed of cobwebs. In fact, if you return to the Zhu Estate above and try jumping in the pit again, you'll end up in this very spot!
